{"tid":1581990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岳義士最新消息 3 - 謝絕籌款活動","createTime":"2019-09-20T00:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T09:25:55.000Z","uid":229411,"like":326,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"b63014c486f1cb6fe2633a2a983b465e5b3149ae","tid":1581990,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:20:57.000Z","msg":"由於岳義士同家人希望低調處理，現階段完全無需要為佢公開籌款，希望大家留意返。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;感謝大家<br />\n我是岳義士本人<br />\n網上消息指有人以我名義發動籌款，本人再次重申並無籌款需要。經諮詢律師意見後，特別撰寫這聲明澄清，若有人繼續以本人名義進行籌款，本人將保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n而本人將會日後再向大家公佈<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都很關心我，謝謝各位手足，香港人繼續加油。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/513582896072061?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F161014811328873%2Fposts%2F513582896072061%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=3b34e4ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/161014811328873/posts/513582896072061?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"3a9581441923c735ab3976f5e5ae227ed08df52e","tid":1581990,"uid":62799,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:04.000Z","msg":"推！感謝岳義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人一生平安！"},{"pid":"16e9cc06807667b09a6fadfd1679685d7d7b039c","tid":1581990,"uid":229411,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5yL2QC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5yL2QC.jpg&h=f684f150&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"584cf2eac1ba79cb8d2bf5a3c8ff135655f428b5","tid":1581990,"uid":263219,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:59.000Z","msg":"頂，咁好既男人邊到搵"},{"pid":"36a0fa1d21155b2c038cb5d9f073162bda168f8b","tid":1581990,"uid":177338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:23:28.000Z","msg":"push 岳兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"